window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>War is coming.</b></p> <p>Ryan Rosa has built something special in New Realm Online: the most advanced VR game ever. But it isn't a perfect world.</p> <p>Enemy guilds have started to target their friends. Ryan is going to have to work hard to protect his new friends. After re-rolling his original character, Ryan has started to find his groove. With the help of his crazy friends, he is going to protect what is his.</p> <p>This book contains the classic LitRPG elements of leveling, dungeons, terrifying killer bunnies, crafting, and community building.</p>"; 
